<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Bind Affinity</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=354">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=354">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This is a VERY useful spell that will change a character's starting point to a new location. As a result, if that person travels a great distance to a different city (i.e., Freeport to Qeynos), and then is bound to that location, and subsequently dies, they will start in the newly bound area. This spell will prevent a lot of aggravation and will make any character that needs it your new best friend!<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Self: Set Home Point<BR>
Target: Must be grouped to Bind another
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
			Casting Time:<br>
			Target Type:<br>
			Level:<br>
			Rank:<br>
    </font></td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">

		  &nbsp;<br>
		  &nbsp;<br>
			100<br>
			6<br>
			Target<br>
			14<br>
			4<br>
    </font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Availble to:</b></font><br>
    
					<a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=19&mode=details&type=races'>Wizard</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=10&mode=details&type=races'>Magician</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=1&mode=details&type=races'>Druid</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=12&mode=details&type=races'>Necromancer</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=17&mode=details&type=races'>Shaman</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=9&mode=details&type=races'>Cleric</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=3&mode=details&type=races'>Enchanter</a>
    
